title: Side chair
provenance: Gift of Tetsuzo Inumaru, President and General Manager, Imperial Hotel, Tokyo, Japan (c. 1935-1968). (Hotel demolished in 1968.)
description: Side chair with octagonal seat, hexagonal back supported by three central vertical members which rise from seat stretcher. Slanting legs form triangular voids and irregular hexagonal voids at intersections with stretchers. Slip seat and back panel covered in yellow chintz (reproduction).
name: Side chair
